# @COMMENT: This fragment is not found in HSNX. It recounts how ʿUmar b. al-Khaṭṭāb distribute charity during the Year of the Drought (Ramādah), which occurred in the year 18 during a major drought (see SFTXV01P138C). Also see WBSAB, WABAW, WAKMW, and WSFAB for a reference to the event. @EC_02/28/23@

